NodeStatusBar includes or can use the Hysteria client binary.

Hysteria
- Upstream: https://github.com/apernet/hysteria
- Website: https://v2.hysteria.network/
- License: MIT

The bundled binary is provided for convenience. You can replace it with a
locally installed Hysteria executable at /opt/homebrew/bin/hysteria or
/usr/local/bin/hysteria.
